{
  "stem": "3631.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he transferred me to another barrack, which was a little better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I managed to get-- get along with them, maybe because I was good in what I did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- in other words, I was able to write the letters that they wanted, and when they wanted it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was not an easy job, because-- it sounds like a cushy job-- gee, you work at an office when it's cold outside-- it wasn't like this, because you were under their eyes all the time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You had no office hours, no regular hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They could come at 1:00 at night and pull you out, and come to the office, and you work all through for two days and nights without coming back to your barrack again if they wanted to do this.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was not easy at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother worked in the-- in one of the clothes-- the Plaszow factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she worked harder than all of us because she had to work night shift.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- she was, by that time, a woman in her 50s, and-- with white hair.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was not easy, and a lot of things happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at one time, there was 5,000 women from night shift were transported out to other camps, and somehow, by a miracle, my mother was not taken.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some other time in transport was, we would hide our parents in our barracks under our little pillows that we had, and we would just hide them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or when the-- if people were called by barrack and when we knew they were in barrack number 13, and then we took them into barrack number 8, they'd know she-- she wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
